  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ZIMCODD: SA Solidarity hub Ubumbano voice app host</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Ubumbano app will equip community members, the media and other stakeholders to utilize different social media networks to tell their own narrative. It is also envisaged that this application will influence decision makers and strengthen calls for accountability from authorities.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ZIMCODD acts as hosts of the moderator, whose job it is to manage the stories from communities through the app and website.
The Mobile application will give regular updates which interested parties can consume on the go and can respond or give feedback within a short timeframe, thus encouraging dialogue and transparency. The application will also take advantage of existing social platforms to create a more integrated approach to information consumption.</narrative>
  </description>
